---
title: Roasted Squash Alfredo Linguine with Ricotta and Fried Sage
description: The ultimate veggie-based comfort food for when your soul needs a little boost! This creamy, luscious pasta dish is filled with roasted butternut squash, cream and ricotta that clings to delightfully fresh linguine! Top it all off with some toasted almonds and fried sage and dinner is served!
